EN: People appreciate fair judgments.

ZH: 这家公司注重对待员工的公道。
EN: This company values fairness in dealing with employees.

ZH: 我们应该为所有人提供公道的机会。
EN: We should provide equal opportunities for everyone.

ZH: 她要求公道对待所有的学生。
EN: She demands fair treatment for all students.

ZH: 法庭需要确保每个人都能得到公道。
EN: The court needs to ensure justice for everyone.

ZH: 我们都需要一个公道的系统来解决争议。
EN: We all need a fair system to resolve disputes.

ZH: 公道的法律能够保护弱势群体的权益。
EN: Fair laws can protect the rights of marginalized groups.

ZH: 他的态度十分公道，从不偏袒任何一方。
EN: His attitude is very fair, never favoring any party.

